Trade/Device Name(s): PC care™ Blood Glucose Data Management Software
Regulation Name(s): Calculator/data processing module for clinical use
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for PC care™ Blood Glucose Data Management Software as a PC-based accessory for i-SENS blood glucose meters to review, analyze, and manage glucose test results.
Indications for Use Summary: PC-based software intended for home and professional use to assist people with diabetes and healthcare professionals in reviewing, analyzing, and evaluating glucose test results for diabetes management, by connecting to i-SENS blood glucose meter for automated data download.
